  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.19.0\n\n### What happened?\n\nWhile working on a Hardhat project that includes `@openzeppelin/contracts` as a dependency, I encountered an issue when attempting to flatten the `ProxyAdmin.sol` file. The command used was `npx hardhat flatten ./node_modules/@openzeppelin/contracts/proxy/transparent/ProxyAdmin.sol > ProxyAdmin.sol`. Instead of successfully flattening the file, Hardhat returned the following error:\r\n\r\n```\r\nError HH1006: The file /Users/usr/project/node_modules/@openzeppelin/contracts/proxy/transparent/ProxyAdmin.sol is treated as local but is inside a node_modules directory\r\n```\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\n1. Initialize a Hardhat project and install `@openzeppelin/contracts` as a dependency.\r\n2. Run the command `npx hardhat flatten ./node_modules/@openzeppelin/contracts/proxy/transparent/ProxyAdmin.sol > ProxyAdmin.sol`.\r\n3. Observe the error HH1006 being thrown.\r\n\n\n### Search terms\n\nHardhat error HH1006 Flattening node_modules contracts",
